(9, 1, '2015-02-09 02:13:43', '2015-02-09 02:13:43', '<p>你的名字 （必填）<br />\n    [text* your-name] </p>\n\n<p>你的邮箱 （必填）<br />\n    [email* your-email] </p>\n\n<p>主题<br />\n    [text your-subject] </p>\n\n<p>你的留言<br />\n    [textarea your-message] </p>\n\n<p>[submit "发送"]</p>\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <admin@foo.com>\n发件人：[your-name] <[your-email]>\n主题：[your-subject]\n\n留言正文：\n[your-message]\n\n--\n这封邮件通过联系表单【百分留学网 (http://localhost/schools100)】发送\nadmin@foo.com\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n0\n0\n\n[your-subject]\n百分留学网 <admin@foo.com>\n留言正文：\n[your-message]\n\n--\n这封邮件通过联系表单【百分留学网 (http://localhost/schools100)】发送\n[your-email]\nReply-To: admin@foo.com\n\n0\n0\n你的留言已经成功发送。谢谢\n你的留言发送失败。请稍后再尝试发送或者使用其他方法联系管理员。\n出现验证错误。请检查所有内容，再重新提交。\n你的留言发送失败。请稍后再尝试发送或者使用其他方法联系管理员。\n请接受条款，然后进行下一步。\nPlease fill in the required field.\nThis input is too long.\nThis input is too short.', '联系表单 1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e8%81%94%e7%b3%bb%e8%a1%a8%e5%8d%95-1', '', '', '2015-02-09 02:13:43', '2015-02-09 02:13:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/schools100/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&p=9', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
